### Test Statistics and Overview APIs
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### ============================================
### REVENUE & STATISTICS APIs
### ============================================

### 1. Get Revenue Statistics (Daily)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/revenue/statistics?startDate=2025-12-01&endDate=2025-12-22&timeFrame=daily
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Get Revenue Statistics (Weekly)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/revenue/statistics?startDate=2025-12-01&endDate=2025-12-22&timeFrame=weekly
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Get Revenue Statistics (Monthly)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/revenue/statistics?startDate=2025-12-01&endDate=2025-12-22&timeFrame=monthly
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Get Revenue by Payment Method
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/revenue/by-payment-method?startDate=2025-12-01&endDate=2025-12-22
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Get Total Revenue
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/revenue/total?startDate=2025-12-01&endDate=2025-12-22
Content-Type: application/json

### ============================================
### ORDER STATISTICS APIs
### ============================================

### 6. Get All Orders (with date filter)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders?startDate=2025-12-01&endDate=2025-12-22
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. Get Orders by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders?status=paid&startDate=2025-12-01&endDate=2025-12-22
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Get Order Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/statistics?startDate=2025-12-01&endDate=2025-12-22
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. Get Top Selling Items
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/top-selling?startDate=2025-12-01&endDate=2025-12-22&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

### ============================================
### REPORT APIs
### ============================================

### 10. Generate Daily Report
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reportType": "daily",
  "date": "2025-12-15",
  "timeFrame": "daily"
}

### 11. Generate Weekly Report
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reportType": "weekly",
  "startDate": "2025-12-01",
  "endDate": "2025-12-07",
  "timeFrame": "weekly"
}

### 12. Generate Monthly Report
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reports/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reportType": "monthly",
  "startDate": "2025-12-01",
  "endDate": "2025-12-31",
  "timeFrame": "monthly"
}

